title: Chore Chore Mastuto Bhai
subTitle: John is hired by Nagraj to steal a diamond but ends up betraying him, inviting his ire. Before Nagraj's henchman kills John, he gives the diamond to a taxi driver for safekeeping.

title: Dhanraj Tamang
subTitle: Dhanraj, an honest labourer, is unable to help his wife from sexual abuse at the hands of his boss. After being jailed on account of false allegations, he returns to exact revenge.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainavati firmly announces that she disagrees with Parvati and Lord Shiva's marriage, while Tarakasura seeks help from Shukracharya to hatch a strategy against Parvati.

title: Kichu Pawa Kichu Chawa
subTitle: Four years after Madhuri's husband, Indrajit, disappears while fighting a war, she marries Uday. However, Indrajit comes back and wants Madhuri, who is pregnant with Uday's baby, to return to him.

title: Pratisodh
subTitle: A malicious leader often sends his men to loot the crops from the helpless peasantry on failure to repay the loan amount. However, a samaritan decides to even the odds.

title: Bondhoo
subTitle: A devoted father stands up to obstacles and fights against all odds to win legal custody of his young son.

title: Baro Bou
subTitle: Tapan and his wife generously provide for their joint family. However, when the younger brother marries his employer's daughter, he becomes arrogant, which creates a rift within the family.

title: Challenge 2
subTitle: ACP Abhiraj Roy, who believes his father is dead, accepts the challenge to catch a dangerous mobster. He soon discovers the source of corruption in the political nexus and decides to end it.

title: Josh
subTitle: Indra, a care-free college student, tries to save his best friend's sister, Anuradha, from a dangerous family dispute, but his efforts lead to unexpected and worsening complications.

title: Golpo Holeo Shotti
subTitle: Rudra is a pizza delivery man who lives with Anuradha, his girlfriend and an aspiring author. However, a horrific incident changes his life when he starts doubting Anuradha's existence.

title: Golpo Holeo Shotti
subTitle: Rudra is a pizza delivery man who lives with Anuradha, his girlfriend and an aspiring author. However, a horrific incident changes his life when he starts doubting Anuradha's existence.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Taraki confronts Parvati and declares a war against her, using her power. Lord Shiva is unable to protect Parvati.

title: Prem O Paap
subTitle: Alokendu and Parvati are in love and hope to marry each other. Parvati loses trust in Alokendu when he escapes an incident, wherein a boy gets killed.

title: Sabuj Saathi
subTitle: Sabuj learns that Sathi, the girl he loves, is his friend Rahul's girlfriend and decides to conceal his feelings for her while secretly doing everything to keep her happy.

title: Ranakshetra
subTitle: When Santu protests against availability of drugs and gets murdered by a minister's son, his brother, Raja decides to seek justice on his own after his legal efforts go in vain.

title: Tulkalam
subTitle: Honest, hard-working villagers fight against the forces of industrialisation threatening to take their land away.

title: Prem Amar
subTitle: A young man falls in love with his new neighbour. However, his life takes a turn for the worse when he learns that she is betrothed to another man.

title: Greftaar
subTitle: Arun Roy, a police sub-inspector, comes face-to-face with a corrupt political leader, Indrajit, and stands up to him. As a result, his father is humiliated and suspended from the police.

title: Maan Maryada
subTitle: Yogesh, a selfless man, takes care and raises his two step-brothers, a step-sister and an orphan boy. However, when things go south and he becomes bankrupt, his step-siblings abandon him.

title: Maan Maryada
subTitle: Yogesh, a selfless man, takes care and raises his two step-brothers, a step-sister and an orphan boy. However, when things go south and he becomes bankrupt, his step-siblings abandon him.

title: Sathi Hara
subTitle: Kundan, a nomad, is offered a music deal when his songs are noticed by a pair of music directors. His lover, Rupa, convinces him to accept it but misunderstandings cause a rift in their relationship.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: To deal with the battle, Parvati takes the form of Adi Shakti and attacks Taraki with fire. Rage and vengeance ignite within Tarakasura.

title: Arshinagar
subTitle: Ranajit and Julekha belong to rival families who have been enemies for years. However, when they meet, there is an unbeatable connection that eventually turns into love.

title: Abbajan
subTitle: A Hindu civil servant's family moves into a predominantly Muslim neighbourhood. Later, when the children befriend a local man, their mother disapproves of their close bond.

title: Aakrosh
subTitle: Samrat, a local thug, constantly protects the people from gangsters like Pannalal. However, many hidden truths about his family tumble out when Subroto, a police officer, is assigned to the area.

title: Phande Poriya Boga Kande Re
subTitle: A light-hearted wedding turns tense when buried family rivalries threaten to explode, testing the resolve of a newly arrived son-in-law.

title: Jamai Raja
subTitle: Realising that marriage is her only path to inheriting her father's fortune, a woman gets married to a poor man who is in desperate need of money.

title: Sasur Bari Zindabad
subTitle: While running away from an arranged marriage, Rupa meets Sonu, a mechanic who changes her life forever.

title: Le Halua Le
subTitle: Sonali moves to the city to earn money and repay her debts to her landlord. She fakes a marriage with Suvojeet, a struggling artist, in order to get low-priced accommodation.
